                        <par_12
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="wcm/foundation/components/parsys">
                            <container4
                                cq:styleIds="[1653545825687,1653545847150,1653242825678,1653545835982,1653545835879]"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/container/v2/container">
                                <text2
                                    cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1659545835858]"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2025-11-05T15:31:54.802-05:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                    text="&lt;p>At AbbVie, our mission to make a positive impact for patients goes beyond the laboratory. It lives in the everyday actions of our Employee Resource Groups (ERGs) – seven communities that advocate for how we approach health care inclusion and innovation.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>With more than 150 chapters worldwide, our ERGs are open to all employees. ERG members bring diverse perspectives that drive meaningful business impact.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                    textIsRich="true"/>
                            </container4>
                            <quote_copy_copy
                                cq:styleIds="[1000000000000]"
                                jcr:created="{Date}2025-09-15T12:27:55.487-04:00"
                                jcr:createdBy="VALENSX5"
                                jcr:lastModified="{Date}2025-11-07T10:33:02.169-05:00"
                                jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/quote"
                                attributionName="Brittany Winstead"
                                attributionTitle="PharmD RPh, Associate Director, Program Management Solid Tumor, AbbVie, and BBN Global Chair"
                                dmPresetType="imagePreset"
                                fileReference="/content/dam/abbvie-com2/images/stories/erg/brittany-winstead-quote-thumbnail.jpg"
                                quote="Through consistent community involvement, we highlight AbbVie’s dedication to transforming lives and empower potential patients by building lasting connections based on integrity and trust."
                                quoteType="regular"
                                textSize="h0"/>
                            <container4_copy
                                cq:styleIds="[1653545847150,1653242825678,1653545825687,1653545835982]"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/container/v2/container">
                                <title2_copy_copy
                                    cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1651545824678,1651545825694]"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2025-11-05T15:36:02.214-05:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    jcr:title="Ability at AbbVie: Supporting Every Journey "
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/title/v2/title"
                                    type="h2"
                                    variant="h"/>
                                <text2
                                    cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1659545835858]"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2025-11-05T15:36:18.352-05:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                    text="&lt;p>Ability at AbbVie creates space for employees and caregivers impacted by neurodiversity, mental health and physical disabilities. These focus areas form Ability’s innovative &amp;quot;Circles” approach, which provides crucial peer support and shares insights and suggested enhancements with leadership.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>For example, when the ERG discovered a gap in wheelchair accessibility for large events with stages, they didn't just identify the problem – they secured approval and funding for equipment that now benefits the entire organization.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>“Our ERG members live with the same disabilities as our patients,” said Jeff C. Mohr, director, Global Portfolio Management, AbbVie, and Ability at AbbVie chair. “Improving employees’ lives is analogous to helping our patients live with their disability.”&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                    textIsRich="true"/>
                                <separator
                                    cq:styleIds="[1662756423318]"
                                    jcr:created="{Date}2025-11-05T15:36:32.117-05:00"
                                    jcr:createdBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2025-11-05T15:36:32.117-05:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/separator/v2/separator"/>
                                <title2_copy_copy_cop
                                    cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1651545824678,1651545825694]"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2025-11-05T15:36:51.400-05:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    jcr:title="AHORA: Creating Inclusive Innovation "
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/title/v2/title"
                                    type="h2"
                                    variant="h"/>
                                <text2_copy
                                    cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1659545835858]"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2025-11-05T15:37:01.615-05:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                    text="&lt;p>AHORA recognizes, celebrates and educates others about&amp;nbsp;Latino and Hispanic culture. It has expanded from a cultural networking group into a community that helps employees by harnessing collective strengths and supporting personal and professional journeys – and drives impact by sharing insights with AbbVie business teams.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&amp;quot;We are seeing leaders gain confidence and operate with a larger impact focus versus just a business focus,&amp;quot; said Nelson Caudillo, associate director, BTS Workforce Enablement, AbbVie, and AHORA chair. “Through our efforts we have raised awareness of AbbVie in the community, which helps us expand our talent pool.”&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                    textIsRich="true"/>
                                <separator_copy
                                    cq:styleIds="[1662756423318]"
                                    jcr:created="{Date}2025-11-05T15:36:32.117-05:00"
                                    jcr:createdBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2025-11-05T15:36:32.117-05:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/separator/v2/separator"/>
                                <title2_copy_copy_cop_1541639023
                                    cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1651545824678,1651545825694]"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2025-11-05T15:37:23.810-05:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    jcr:title="Asian Leadership Network: Building Bridges to Better Health "
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/title/v2/title"
                                    type="h2"
                                    variant="h"/>
                                <text2_copy_copy
                                    cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1659545835858]"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2025-11-05T15:37:40.077-05:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                    text="&lt;p>Asian Leadership Network (ALN) exemplifies how ERGs help AbbVie advance clinical trial awareness through a partnership with AbbVie's Patient Inclusion team.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&amp;quot;It is through communication, engagement and education that we can connect with our communities and patient populations that represent the real world,&amp;quot; said Kavita R. Sail, senior director, Health Economics Outcomes Research, AbbVie, and ALN co-chair. The ERG's recent clinical trial awareness event drew nearly 300 attendees.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                    textIsRich="true"/>
                                <separator_copy_copy
                                    cq:styleIds="[1662756423318]"
                                    jcr:created="{Date}2025-11-05T15:36:32.117-05:00"
                                    jcr:createdBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2025-11-05T15:36:32.117-05:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/separator/v2/separator"/>
                                <title2_copy_copy_cop_1120408144
                                    cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1651545824678,1651545825694]"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2025-11-05T15:38:02.112-05:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    jcr:title="Black Business Network: Amplifying Our Voices "
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/title/v2/title"
                                    type="h2"
                                    variant="h"/>
                                <text2_copy_copy_copy
                                    cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1659545835858]"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2025-11-05T15:38:16.560-05:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                    text="&lt;p>Black Business Network (BBN) demonstrates the power of authentic community engagement. Its partnership with the African American Male Wellness Agency, which works to expand the life expectancy of African American men, goes beyond traditional corporate outreach.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>“Through consistent community involvement, we highlight AbbVie’s dedication to transforming lives and empower potential patients by building lasting connections based on integrity and trust,” said Brittany Winstead, PharmD RPh, Associate Director, Program Management Solid Tumor, AbbVie, and BBN Global Chair.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>BBN’s approach helps AbbVie understand health disparities and cultural factors that impact health care access, informing more effective outreach strategies.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                    textIsRich="true"/>
                                <separator_copy_copy_
                                    cq:styleIds="[1662756423318]"
                                    jcr:created="{Date}2025-11-05T15:36:32.117-05:00"
                                    jcr:createdBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2025-11-05T15:36:32.117-05:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/separator/v2/separator"/>
                                <title2_copy_copy_cop_1601242586
                                    cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1651545824678,1651545825694]"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2025-11-05T15:39:23.487-05:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    jcr:title="AbbVie PRIDE: Celebrating Authentic Selves "
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/title/v2/title"
                                    type="h2"
                                    variant="h"/>
                                <text2_copy_copy_copy_422964809
                                    cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1659545835858]"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2025-11-05T15:39:34.248-05:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                    text="&lt;p>AbbVie PRIDE supports employees, including LGBTQ+, through meaningful community engagement. During Pride Month in June 2025, PRIDE leaders marched in seven parades globally, from Tokyo to Chicago. Additionally, they created a playbook to help managers better understand the LGBTQ+ talent experience.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>“At the Out for Undergrad conference, we connected with high-achieving LGBTQ+ students from 76 schools to help build AbbVie’s future pipeline,” said Debbie Tan, director, Regulatory Portfolio Management, AbbVie, and PRIDE chair.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                    textIsRich="true"/>
                                <separator_copy_copy__143223646
                                    cq:styleIds="[1662756423318]"
                                    jcr:created="{Date}2025-11-05T15:36:32.117-05:00"
                                    jcr:createdBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2025-11-05T15:36:32.117-05:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/separator/v2/separator"/>
                                <title2_copy_copy_cop_580624910
                                    cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1651545824678,1651545825694]"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2025-11-05T15:39:55.155-05:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    jcr:title="AbbVie Veterans: Serving in a New Way "
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/title/v2/title"
                                    type="h2"
                                    variant="h"/>
                                <text2_copy_copy_copy_556000115
                                    cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1659545835858]"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2025-11-05T15:40:08.799-05:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                    text="&lt;p>AbbVie Veterans ERG (VERG) has embedded something truly meaningful: the SkillBridge program from the U.S. Department of Defense. The initiative helps transitioning service members find their place at AbbVie, with a 63% hire rate in 2024.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&amp;quot;This is just one of the life-changing opportunities AbbVie provides,&amp;quot; said one manager of a recent SkillBridge associate.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                    textIsRich="true"/>
                                <separator_copy_copy__446164148
                                    cq:styleIds="[1662756423318]"
                                    jcr:created="{Date}2025-11-05T15:36:32.117-05:00"
                                    jcr:createdBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2025-11-05T15:36:32.117-05:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/separator/v2/separator"/>
                                <title2_copy_copy_cop_1655769388
                                    cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1651545824678,1651545825694]"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2025-11-05T15:40:26.663-05:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    jcr:title="Women Leaders in Action: Leading Global Change "
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/title/v2/title"
                                    type="h2"
                                    variant="h"/>
                                <text2_copy_copy_copy_322319298
                                    cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1659545835858]"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2025-11-05T15:40:40.801-05:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                    text="&lt;p>Women Leaders in Action (WLA) is AbbVie's largest ERG with chapters around the world. Beyond its global mentorship programs, WLA is ensuring its communications are translated in multiple languages, enabling its reach to broader audiences.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&amp;quot;Knowledge and awareness are empowering, and that's precisely what we achieve through multilingual communications,&amp;quot; said Christine M. Coulombe, vice president, Parkinson’s Disease, AbbVie, and WLA chair. “One ERG’s innovation can amplify our collective impact.”&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                    textIsRich="true"/>
                            </container4_copy>
                        </par_12>
